Anyways  everyone play safely.No bao Jiak thing one.No sure thing  our market affected by many factors.Recently market is indeed better  but still . Practice vigilance  always have a SL in mind . That’s the difference being able to survive or becoming a goner in just 1 bad trade.Easy said but not easily done. But always good to remind ourselves. 🙏Last time  I’ve always provided daily reminders on Stop Loss. But think people all see those daily morning greetings also sianz.Anyways  SL it’s up to oneself. Because some times kenna stopped out   then counter run.That’s why  whatever decisions we make when we trade  must take own responsibility. That’s the only way one can improve.BBs been quite generous recently  but guess what  it’s nothing new eventually they gonna wanna take it all back and more too.Therefore  always be practical and react accordingly to market and sentiments.DYODD at all times  OSOD  OTOT on your stop loss/TP. (Let it be constant reminder to oneself)🙏🙏🙏
